          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Tax Relief for our Nation's Heroes Act or the Andrew P. Carpenter Tax Act </strong></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to exclude from gross income any amount attributable to the discharge of student loan indebtedness of a veteran who served on active duty and: (1) is deceased as a result of a service-connected death or disability, or (2) has a service-connected disability that the Department of Veterans Affairs has rated as total. </p> <p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2017-01-12T05:00:00Z</updateDate>
